jJExAHeVo4.name: How to Play
jJExAHeVo4.message:
Controls:

READ THIS PLEASE

Move WASD/Arrow Keys
Pick up E Picks up item under you.
Wand 1 R Uses the wand in wand slot 1
Wand 2 T Uses the wand in wand slot 2
Drop G Drops the item selected
Interact B Interacts with any interactable npc or shop
Salvage P Salvages the item you are holding in front of the artificer
Dash Space Gives you a speed boost of 1.5x for 1.5 seconds

All items have a set type, such as "Wand", "Book" or "Potion", which go into their respective slots. Books can be used in any slot, Equippables such as wands, cloaks, artifacts and relics must be placed in their respective slots or else they WILL NOT WORK. The potion slot automatically uses the selected potion on necessity, such as low health or running out of mana.
